title: Fitna NEW VERSION flv files
description:
On Sunday, April 6 2008 Geert Wilders published a new version of his movie Fitna on Liveleak.

In the new version, some images for which the copyright was contested, have been replaced by other images.

This torrent contains the FLV files as they are published on Liveleak.  Just to save you the trouble from finding out how to download them from Liveleak.

English and Dutch versions.

Feel free to convert to other formats and redistribute.
